name: Madhuri Michele Fremont
what_you_do: Madhuri Michèle works with solopreneurs, business professionals, coaches, speakers, and course creators, to go to the next level in their businesses. She delivers results through group programs, masterminds, and one-on-one mentoring.
who_you_serve: solopreneurs, business professionals, coaches, speakers, and course creators
social_proof: Madhuri Michèle graduated with a BS in Industrial Design. She is an expert in project management and is grounded in aesthetics, function, and logical discipline. Proof of this is her product development business, which spanned 25 years. Madhuri received entrepreneurial certification from the renowned CEO Space program. Madhuri is the vice-chairman of the Rhode Island chapter of Mensa.
audience_type: solopreneurs, business professionals, coaches, speakers, course creators
business_focus: Helping solopreneurs, business professionals, coaches, speakers, and course creators go to the next level in their businesses.
